This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modeling research and proposes a novel speedup technique for maximum entropy models. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses machine learning techniques and their training. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with modeling language and predicting words. It may also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it mentions the use of neural networks for language modeling. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.SD (Software Engineering) as it proposes a technique for speeding up the training of machine learning models.
